    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Friend<add>?</add><lb/> I hand you above
                my<lb/> check on Mechanic Bank <placeName>New York</placeName><lb/> for Ninety Seven
                    7<hi rend="underline">4</hi> Dollars for collecting<lb/> to date of Occident
                &amp; Jewish <sic>publication</sic><lb/> Society, please send by return mail<lb/>
                Bill of <persName>David Lopez</persName> to date, as he says<lb/> he has paid you
                some money for the<lb/> O, &amp; the bill I printed he says is not right</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mr Warners</persName>
                <date>July</date> no of the <sic>occident</sic> did<lb/> not come here did you send
                it <add>?</add>,<lb/> send me also bill of <persName>M Lazarus</persName> for Voice
                of<lb/> Jacob &amp; the <sic>sucessor</sic> to it, or has the Journal<lb/> ceased,?
                as I have not received a number for<lb/> a long while, Hoping you are well</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p><add>?</add> your ob<add>?</add><lb/> &amp; friend</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Samuel Hart Sen</persName>
            </p>
            <p>P. S send me some more ½ or a<lb/> dozen copies of the Hebrew<lb/> vocabulary—<lb/>
                <date>Sunday the 22 July 1849</date></p>
            <p>please see that my sisters Donation<lb/> is remitted in the same way to its<lb/>
                destination</p>
            <pb n="2R"/>
            <p>Collections on a<lb/>c Jewish Publication Society<lb/>
                <persName>Miss C Moise</persName> in full $2.<lb/>
                <persName>Mrs N Hart</persName> 1<lb/> " <persName>S. Woolf</persName> 1<lb/> "
                    <persName>B. D Lazarus</persName> 1<lb/> " <persName>S N Hart</persName>
                <hi rend="underline">1.</hi><lb/> $6<lb/> less commission <hi rend="underline"
                    >60</hi><lb/> 5.40</p>
            <p>Collections on a<lb/>c Occident<lb/>
                <persName>C Sampson</persName>
                <placeName>Orangeburg</placeName>. 9.00<lb/>
                <persName>Isaiah Moses</persName>
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName> 3<lb/>
                <persName>Mrs. Jane Warner</persName> — 3.<lb/>
                <persName>Mr M. Mordecai</persName> " 6<lb/> " <persName>Michl Lazarus</persName> —
                6<lb/> " <persName>S A Benjamin</persName> — 3<lb/>
                <persName>Miss H. Hart</persName> ..... <hi rend="underline">3</hi><lb/> $33<lb/>
                less commission <hi rend="underline">5.50 $27 50</hi><lb/> $32.90<lb/> premium on
                Exchange <hi rend="underline">16</hi><lb/> $32 74<lb/> Donation of <persName>Miss
                    Henrietta Hart</persName><lb/> for Our Poor <sic>Bretheren</sic> of
                    <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName>
                <hi rend="underline">5</hi><lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">$37.74</hi></p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
                <date>July 23 1849</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Samuel Hart Senr.</persName>
            </p>
